---
layout: base.njk
title: "All Subjects"
description: "Browse UPSC GS subjects — Polity, Economy, Geography, History, Environment, Science, IR, Society, Ethics, Security. Foundation to Mains depth."
---

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a><span class="breadcrumb__sep">/</span>
      Subjects
    </nav>
    <p class="page-header__eyebrow">Study by Subject</p>
    <h1 class="page-header__title">Choose Your Subject</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">Each subject has notes at three depth levels — Foundation, Prelims, and Mains. Start anywhere based on your preparation stage.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding:var(--space-8) 0;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap:var(--space-6);">
      {% for subj in subjects %}
      <a href="/subjects/{{ subj.slug }}/" class="card" style="text-decoration:none; border-left:4px solid {{ subj.color }};">
        <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:var(--space-3); margin-bottom:var(--space-3);">
          <span style="font-size:2rem;">{{ subj.icon }}</span>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:var(--text-lg); font-weight:var(--font-bold); color:{{ subj.color }};">{{ subj.name }}</h3>
            <div style="margin-top:2px;">
              {% for paper in subj.gs_papers %}
              <span class="gs-badge gs-badge--{{ paper }}" style="font-size:0.6rem;">{{ paper | upper }}</span>
              {% endfor %}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="card__desc">{{ subj.description }}</p>
        <div style="margin-top:var(--space-3); font-size:var(--text-xs); color:var(--color-text-muted);">
          {{ collections.allTopics | countBySubject(subj.slug) }} topics available
        </div>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
